df%>%
  filter(death==1)%>%

df%>%
  filter(sex==1|sex==2)%>%

df%>%
  ggplot(aes(x=admtype, fill=asource))+geom_bar()

dfa<-df%>%
  filter(death==0 | death==1)%>%
  mutate(quarter=case_when(moa==1 | moa==2 | moa==3 ~1,
                       moa==4 | moa==5 | moa==6 ~2,
                       moa==7 | moa==8 | moa==9 ~3,
                       moa==10 | moa==11 | moa==12 ~4)) %>%
  mutate(yearquarter=paste(yoa, quarter, sep="-"))%>%
  select(yearquarter, death, los, age)%>%
  drop_na()%>%
  group_by(yearquarter, death)%>%
  summarise(avgage=mean(age), avglos=mean(los))%>%
  rowid_to_column('ID')%>%
  filter(ID<32)
ggplot(dfa, aes(x=ID, y=avgage, color=death))+geom_line(size=4)+scale_x_discrete(name ="Year", limits=c("2015","2016","2017", "2018"))+transition_reveal(ID)

dfb<-df %>%
  mutate(icu=as.numeric(icu))%>%
  filter(los<100 & los>=0)%>%
  filter(age>65 & age<200)%>%
  mutate(icuFlag=case_when(icu == 0~"No",
                           TRUE~"Yes"))%>%
  filter(death==1)%>%
  filter(icuFlag=="Yes" | icuFlag=="No")
ggplot(dfb, aes(x=age, y=los, color=sex, shape=icuFlag, aplha=0.8))+geom_jitter()

set.seed(1738)
dfmodel<-df%>%
  filter(yoa>15)%>%
  filter(sex==1 | sex==2)%>%
  mutate(icu=as.numeric(icu))%>%
  mutate(yearmonth=paste(yoa, moa, sep="-"))%>%
  mutate(icuFlag=case_when(icu == 0~"No",
                           TRUE~"Yes"))%>%
  filter(admtype==1|admtype==2|admtype==3|admtype==4|admtype==5)%>%
  filter(payer!="Y" & payer!="Z" & payer!="X")%>%
  filter(asource!="X" & asource != "V" & asource != "U")%>%
  select(target=death, icuFlag, yearmonth, age, sex, raceethn, provider, admtype, asource, service, payer, drg)%>%
  drop_na()

library(caret)
splitIndex <- createDataPartition(dfmodel$target, p = .70, list = FALSE, times = 1)
train <- dfmodel[ splitIndex,]
test <- dfmodel[-splitIndex,]

library(ranger)
train0 = train[train$target == '0',]
train1 = train[train$target == '1',]
n0 = nrow(train0)
n1 = nrow(train1)
train00 = train0[sample(1:n0, n1),]
train_under = rbind(train00, train1)
model <- train(target~.,data =train_under, method = "rpart2")
pred=predict(model,test)
cmRpart2=confusionMatrix(pred, test$target, positive="1")
model <- train(target~.,data =train_under, method = "ranger")
pred=predict(model,test)
cmRanger=confusionMatrix(pred, test$target, positive="1")
model <- train(target~.,data =train_under, method = "LogitBoost")
pred=predict(model,test)
cmlogreg=confusionMatrix(pred, test$target, positive="1")
model <- train(target~.,data =train_under, method = "LMT")
pred=predict(model,test)
cmLMT=confusionMatrix(pred, test$target, positive="1")
model <- train(target~.,data =train_under, method = "nnet")
pred=predict(model,test)
cmNnet=confusionMatrix(pred, test$target, positive="1")
Outputs<-data.frame(c("LMT","LogReg","Nnet","Ranger","Rpart2"),c(cmLMT$overall["Accuracy"], cmlogreg$overall["Accuracy"], cmNnet$overall["Accuracy"], cmRanger$overall["Accuracy"], cmRpart2$overall["Accuracy"]), c(cmLMT$byClass["Balanced Accuracy"], cmlogreg$byClass["Balanced Accuracy"], cmNnet$byClass["Balanced Accuracy"], cmRanger$byClass["Balanced Accuracy"], cmRpart2$byClass["Balanced Accuracy"]))
names(Outputs)<-c("model", "accuracy", "balanced accuracy")
